    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en">Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'female fertile' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'female fertility'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0000888.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
